1
00:00:00,433 --> 00:00:01,633
welcome back

2
00:00:01,966 --> 00:00:05,166
today we are going to sift through the UMV tier

3
00:00:05,266 --> 00:00:07,633
however before doing any of that

4
00:00:07,633 --> 00:00:10,033
we have to fix our power production

5
00:00:10,033 --> 00:00:12,633
while it looks like we are doing fine

6
00:00:12,633 --> 00:00:14,200
we are actually not

7
00:00:14,400 --> 00:00:17,033
our wireless network is indeed empty

8
00:00:17,100 --> 00:00:20,366
so empty that our plasma mixer can't work

9
00:00:20,366 --> 00:00:23,400
it just received 10 minutes of stocked up power

10
00:00:23,400 --> 00:00:25,566
but it is draining it in no time

11
00:00:25,766 --> 00:00:28,500
so we should build a second Dyson sphere

12
00:00:28,500 --> 00:00:30,200
since it won't be the last one

13
00:00:30,200 --> 00:00:33,200
and each one requires many different parts

14
00:00:33,200 --> 00:00:35,233
we shall make a custom AE2 pattern

15
00:00:35,233 --> 00:00:38,500
to prepare all of its components with a single click

16
00:00:38,566 --> 00:00:38,900
and there

17
00:00:38,900 --> 00:00:42,200
we have the total cost of each of those structures

18
00:00:42,200 --> 00:00:44,000
once the structure is built

19
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:45,466
we can go back to our base

20
00:00:45,466 --> 00:00:46,200
and remember that

21
00:00:46,200 --> 00:00:48,800
we can also turn on our backup generators

22
00:00:48,800 --> 00:00:50,266
to get an extra kick

23
00:00:50,300 --> 00:00:50,633
sadly

24
00:00:50,633 --> 00:00:54,100
we didn't hit the 1 trillion production milestone

25
00:00:54,266 --> 00:00:54,933
fear not

26
00:00:54,933 --> 00:00:57,433
that was the end of the fuels

27
00:00:57,433 --> 00:01:00,000
but there is still more room in the future

28
00:01:00,200 --> 00:01:02,600
and with the future of fuels

29
00:01:02,600 --> 00:01:05,033
we can almost double the milestone

30
00:01:05,166 --> 00:01:07,833
now that we have some more energy to work with

31
00:01:07,833 --> 00:01:10,033
we can start our new quests

32
00:01:10,166 --> 00:01:12,900
after quickly completing the usual components

33
00:01:12,900 --> 00:01:16,400
we will probably want to get a component assembly line upgrade

34
00:01:16,400 --> 00:01:19,666
to reduce the spacetime and hypogen costs

35
00:01:19,766 --> 00:01:20,466
however

36
00:01:20,466 --> 00:01:23,600
it looks like hard metals is not the thing we lack of

37
00:01:23,700 --> 00:01:27,066
we are short on the polymer made by exotic bacteria

38
00:01:27,233 --> 00:01:28,700
to skip the whole chemistry

39
00:01:28,700 --> 00:01:30,800
we would need a tier four QFT

40
00:01:30,800 --> 00:01:34,333
which however costs too many UMV components

41
00:01:34,333 --> 00:01:36,400
so we go back to our clean room

42
00:01:36,400 --> 00:01:38,200
where we mutate more bacteria

43
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:40,833
that we then place in some new vats

44
00:01:40,900 --> 00:01:41,766
meanwhile

45
00:01:41,766 --> 00:01:44,766
we can produce a couple of high tier materials

46
00:01:44,766 --> 00:01:47,266
we add one more step to our circuitry

47
00:01:47,366 --> 00:01:50,466
and we get the last of the UMV components

48
00:01:50,566 --> 00:01:52,633
then we make the new superconductors

49
00:01:52,633 --> 00:01:54,033
for the new energy hatch

50
00:01:54,033 --> 00:01:56,200
which we can now make wireless

51
00:01:56,300 --> 00:01:58,066
and to get this one

52
00:01:58,066 --> 00:02:01,366
we had to craft all the previous wireless ones

53
00:02:01,400 --> 00:02:05,300
so let's stop for a moment and go all the way back

54
00:02:05,366 --> 00:02:06,233
to start off

55
00:02:06,233 --> 00:02:08,600
we needed the new superconductor

56
00:02:08,666 --> 00:02:12,266
which this time contains Dragon blood and space time

57
00:02:12,566 --> 00:02:14,400
to make it superconducting

58
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:16,433
we can no longer use helium

59
00:02:16,566 --> 00:02:18,500
space time is mandatory

60
00:02:18,766 --> 00:02:22,400
but with that we only got the normal UMV energy hatch

61
00:02:22,500 --> 00:02:24,000
to make it wireless

62
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:26,233
other than a bunch of expensive stuff

63
00:02:26,233 --> 00:02:28,300
we need to do some research

64
00:02:28,366 --> 00:02:29,800
which was recursive

65
00:02:29,966 --> 00:02:33,433
all the way down to a ULV wireless energy hatch

66
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:36,400
but while we have UMV energy hatches

67
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:38,633
we don't have any ULV one

68
00:02:38,866 --> 00:02:39,966
once we get it

69
00:02:39,966 --> 00:02:42,633
we have to research and craft all of the other tiers

70
00:02:42,633 --> 00:02:44,266
back up to UMV

71
00:02:44,633 --> 00:02:47,100
and since our data bank has limited slots

72
00:02:47,100 --> 00:02:49,566
and we are too lazy to make a second one

73
00:02:49,566 --> 00:02:53,200
we started stocking all of the useless stuff in a chest

74
00:02:53,200 --> 00:02:55,466
which is now almost full

75
00:02:55,600 --> 00:02:58,233
then without any recursive research

76
00:02:58,233 --> 00:03:02,600
we also acquired the most powerful wireless hatch we can make so far

77
00:03:02,633 --> 00:03:04,900
UMV 64 amps

78
00:03:05,066 --> 00:03:09,000
this one is as powerful as a 16,000 UV laser hatch

79
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:10,433
but wireless

80
00:03:10,433 --> 00:03:14,166
and its first use should be to speed up our circuit production

81
00:03:14,566 --> 00:03:18,233
so that we can make more than one UXV circuit every minute

82
00:03:18,233 --> 00:03:20,500
instead of one every 15 minutes

83
00:03:20,766 --> 00:03:21,600
meanwhile

84
00:03:21,600 --> 00:03:25,233
we also managed to upgrade our component assembly line

85
00:03:25,366 --> 00:03:28,366
the next quest isn't really a quest but a warning

86
00:03:28,566 --> 00:03:31,266
we could simply Mark it as complete and move on

87
00:03:31,266 --> 00:03:34,033
but I think we should upgrade our base instead

88
00:03:34,066 --> 00:03:35,833
indeed as of now

89
00:03:35,833 --> 00:03:39,900
we are still having trouble crafting just a couple of Dyson Spheres

90
00:03:40,033 --> 00:03:41,666
that's not good at all

91
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:45,900
the first thing we will want to fix is the radox polymer production

92
00:03:46,200 --> 00:03:49,666
and our main objective is to produce it with a QFT

93
00:03:50,100 --> 00:03:52,600
but that requires tier 4 casings

94
00:03:52,600 --> 00:03:55,033
and we have trouble even with crafting the tier 3

95
00:03:55,766 --> 00:03:59,833
so we have to increase the size of our old radox setups

96
00:04:00,166 --> 00:04:02,666
luckily thanks to the Loki ring

97
00:04:02,700 --> 00:04:05,466
we can build many machines at the same time

98
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:08,033
and now we just have to wait a little bit

99
00:04:08,033 --> 00:04:10,066
for some radox to stock up

100
00:04:10,366 --> 00:04:12,866
one other thing required for the tier 4 QFT is

101
00:04:12,866 --> 00:04:15,566
black body Naquadria supersolid

102
00:04:15,566 --> 00:04:17,800
which is made while working Naquadria

103
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:21,400
this process outputs some inert Naquadria dusts

104
00:04:21,400 --> 00:04:23,500
which may not look huge in amount

105
00:04:23,500 --> 00:04:28,400
but we can expand those into thousands of ingots with a neutron activator

106
00:04:28,633 --> 00:04:32,133
the only cost on conversion is a bit of plasma and time

107
00:04:32,133 --> 00:04:37,633
we can shrink the time required by increasing the height of our neutron activators

108
00:04:38,033 --> 00:04:41,033
and thus we shall make those pierce the sky

109
00:04:41,300 --> 00:04:43,566
and that was the tier 3 QFT

110
00:04:43,900 --> 00:04:44,833
for the tier 4

111
00:04:45,200 --> 00:04:47,033
we need more radox polymer

112
00:04:47,366 --> 00:04:48,800
while it stocks up

113
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:52,300
we can work on gathering the other materials we are short on

114
00:04:52,433 --> 00:04:56,033
our old space elevator couldn't stock up enough fluids

115
00:04:56,033 --> 00:04:58,700
so we upgraded its motors and its pumps

116
00:04:58,966 --> 00:05:01,966
while that easily took care of the missing fluids

117
00:05:01,966 --> 00:05:04,233
it won't help with the missing minerals

118
00:05:04,366 --> 00:05:07,266
some ores can't be obtained by space mining

119
00:05:07,500 --> 00:05:10,033
so we have to go back to void miners

120
00:05:10,300 --> 00:05:13,600
but we want to place those in a more special place

121
00:05:13,700 --> 00:05:16,800
the one chosen by the true edgelords like us

122
00:05:17,100 --> 00:05:18,233
to get there

123
00:05:18,233 --> 00:05:21,466
we have to start by compressing a lot of cobblestone

124
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:24,700
so much that we had to upgrade our explosion compressor

125
00:05:24,700 --> 00:05:26,600
to space time and 8 billion EU

126
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:29,200
to get it in a reasonable amount of time

127
00:05:29,433 --> 00:05:31,966
then we cover that cobblestone in cheese

128
00:05:31,966 --> 00:05:34,866
which will act as glue for the other components

129
00:05:34,866 --> 00:05:35,633
finally

130
00:05:35,633 --> 00:05:40,100
we use magic to stick some singularities to that agglomerate

131
00:05:40,100 --> 00:05:40,800
with that

132
00:05:40,800 --> 00:05:42,966
we can now travel to the Promised Land

133
00:05:42,966 --> 00:05:47,200
where void miners will be able to gather any ore that is shown on NEI

134
00:05:47,466 --> 00:05:52,066
so we quickly get a link to the ore processing ae2 subnetwork

135
00:05:52,066 --> 00:05:55,000
and start drilling all of those materials

136
00:05:55,266 --> 00:05:59,000
meanwhile we have managed to complete our tier 4 QFT

137
00:05:59,166 --> 00:06:02,433
which is now making huge amounts of radox polymer

138
00:06:02,933 --> 00:06:05,800
now that Radox Polymer is no longer an issue

139
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:10,400
we can finally start crafting our little project of 10 Dyson Spheres

140
00:06:10,633 --> 00:06:11,133
however

141
00:06:11,133 --> 00:06:14,433
our current base can't handle that puny task

142
00:06:14,566 --> 00:06:16,633
we must do some upgrades

143
00:06:16,666 --> 00:06:20,266
the first thing we want to enchant is our blast furnaces

144
00:06:20,366 --> 00:06:21,866
for some materials

145
00:06:21,866 --> 00:06:24,466
they can barely cook four ingots each second

146
00:06:24,466 --> 00:06:26,900
and the backlog is really huge

147
00:06:26,933 --> 00:06:30,000
so after going inside and do an inspection

148
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:32,033
we decide that the best action to take

149
00:06:32,033 --> 00:06:34,833
is to add some glitter to the heating coils

150
00:06:34,966 --> 00:06:37,500
and then we also increase the power feed

151
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:40,366
now it works 8 times faster

152
00:06:40,433 --> 00:06:44,033
the next thing we have to speed up is our fusion reactors

153
00:06:44,100 --> 00:06:46,266
the Mark 3 were slow to begin with

154
00:06:46,266 --> 00:06:49,966
and the Mark 4 are busy trying to make metastable oganesson

155
00:06:50,133 --> 00:06:53,000
so we are going to craft the fuwusion reactor

156
00:06:53,066 --> 00:06:57,700
you can already tell this is going to be way more powerful from all of its colors

157
00:06:57,833 --> 00:07:00,833
and indeed it's as good as 10 of the previous tier

158
00:07:01,100 --> 00:07:03,566
also for quick recipes

159
00:07:03,566 --> 00:07:06,100
we can manually set the parallel counter

160
00:07:06,400 --> 00:07:09,833
thus making it 100 times faster than the Mark 3

161
00:07:10,400 --> 00:07:13,100
next with a thermosink radiator

162
00:07:13,100 --> 00:07:17,233
we can make our PCB factory 2000 times faster

163
00:07:17,566 --> 00:07:20,066
then to speed up our nanoforge

164
00:07:20,066 --> 00:07:22,166
we made more of those buildings

165
00:07:22,166 --> 00:07:24,666
while also increasing the working power

166
00:07:24,866 --> 00:07:27,066
finally to help our DTPFs

167
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:29,566
we added four more blocks

168
00:07:29,766 --> 00:07:34,000
but all of that caused a huge increase in power consumption

169
00:07:34,400 --> 00:07:36,200
to help our backup generators

170
00:07:36,200 --> 00:07:38,100
we increased the working efficiency

171
00:07:38,100 --> 00:07:39,366
by adding two fluids

172
00:07:39,366 --> 00:07:45,866
that we can obtain by tearing apart some space time using a tesseract and a quantum anomaly on an anvil

173
00:07:46,200 --> 00:07:50,433
and that boost was enough to let us complete the last plasma mixer recipes

174
00:07:50,433 --> 00:07:55,166
thus completing the new generators just in time before we run out of fuel

175
00:07:55,433 --> 00:07:58,833
the old Dyson Spheres took quite some space

176
00:07:58,833 --> 00:08:02,233
so let's try to make the new setup more compact

177
00:08:02,366 --> 00:08:05,766
we figured out we can wall share a bunch of parts

178
00:08:05,966 --> 00:08:08,966
the most important being the computation input

179
00:08:09,066 --> 00:08:11,500
which we are now going to make wireless

180
00:08:11,500 --> 00:08:13,600
thus connecting to the cloud

181
00:08:13,900 --> 00:08:19,100
so that we can keep our computers in our to be data center located in our main base

182
00:08:19,466 --> 00:08:20,566
with that set up

183
00:08:20,566 --> 00:08:22,700
we are now producing more power

184
00:08:22,700 --> 00:08:25,966
but it's still just enough for our update base

185
00:08:26,100 --> 00:08:29,433
so it's clear that we are going to need more

186
00:08:29,700 --> 00:08:31,833
however there is one main issue

187
00:08:31,833 --> 00:08:35,066
we are too slow at producing the spiny ingots

188
00:08:35,166 --> 00:08:38,366
our ebfs indeed can't even make 2 per second

189
00:08:38,366 --> 00:08:39,800
and we need millions

190
00:08:39,800 --> 00:08:41,666
in hope to find a solution

191
00:08:41,666 --> 00:08:44,300
we shall go ask help to some random villagers

192
00:08:44,300 --> 00:08:47,266
who seem to be worshipping some random deities

193
00:08:47,500 --> 00:08:49,833
and it looks like our prayers got answered

194
00:08:49,833 --> 00:08:53,433
all we have to do is build a forge in honor of the gods

195
00:08:53,433 --> 00:08:54,500
we shall make it bigger

196
00:08:54,500 --> 00:08:58,366
and more complex than any other multi block we build so far

197
00:08:58,366 --> 00:08:59,666
to craft it

198
00:08:59,666 --> 00:09:02,366
we are going to search unfindable particles

199
00:09:02,366 --> 00:09:04,633
work weird glitchy materials

200
00:09:04,633 --> 00:09:06,833
and synthesize weird stuff

201
00:09:06,833 --> 00:09:09,200
once all the collection part is done

202
00:09:09,200 --> 00:09:11,766
we proceed into clogging all of our whole base

203
00:09:11,766 --> 00:09:14,900
to craft huge amount of all kind of things

204
00:09:14,966 --> 00:09:18,833
which made us quickly cook huge amounts of old materials

205
00:09:18,866 --> 00:09:25,166
and slowly chug through harder-to-work ones that required a Dyson sphere worth of power to be processed

206
00:09:25,400 --> 00:09:27,233
but given enough time

207
00:09:27,233 --> 00:09:29,433
we managed to process all of that stuff

208
00:09:29,433 --> 00:09:31,433
and complete our new forge

209
00:09:31,733 --> 00:09:34,633
and that thing isn't big just on the outside

210
00:09:34,833 --> 00:09:36,866
it is also a big inside

211
00:09:37,100 --> 00:09:40,033
the first thing we shall read is the nice introduction

212
00:09:40,033 --> 00:09:42,900
that will explain us how that machine works

213
00:09:43,066 --> 00:09:44,966
but the thing we care about the most

214
00:09:44,966 --> 00:09:47,833
is the path to the celestial transcendence

215
00:09:47,966 --> 00:09:50,666
this will help us upgrade our forge

216
00:09:50,833 --> 00:09:51,433
furthermore

217
00:09:51,433 --> 00:09:55,366
we have to start from the start if we want it to even be usable

218
00:09:55,500 --> 00:09:56,766
to do this upgrade

219
00:09:56,766 --> 00:09:59,700
we are going to need some additional materials

220
00:09:59,966 --> 00:10:01,700
which we quickly gather and send

221
00:10:01,700 --> 00:10:03,833
to complete the first upgrade

222
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:05,166
with that done

223
00:10:05,166 --> 00:10:07,366
we can now add our first module

224
00:10:07,366 --> 00:10:09,800
the Helioflare Power Forge

225
00:10:10,233 --> 00:10:14,400
this module is going to work exactly like a blast furnace or a volcano

226
00:10:14,400 --> 00:10:17,066
and now that everything is built

227
00:10:17,066 --> 00:10:18,800
it is time to turn it on

228
00:10:19,166 --> 00:10:20,166
to do so

229
00:10:20,166 --> 00:10:21,733
we make some star fuel

230
00:10:21,733 --> 00:10:23,500
and give it to our forge

231
00:10:23,633 --> 00:10:27,233
then we will be supplying transcendent residue to keep it running

232
00:10:27,466 --> 00:10:30,300
and thus we can now admire our forge spinning

233
00:10:30,466 --> 00:10:33,100
but it's still not at the peak of its glory

234
00:10:33,300 --> 00:10:37,300
indeed we can make the star on the inside more bright and colorful

235
00:10:37,466 --> 00:10:41,633
and I think we can now take one good minute to admire our new machinery

236
00:11:37,700 --> 00:11:41,300
and it turns out that this is not even its final form

237
00:11:41,633 --> 00:11:45,200
but getting the evolution is going to be a more complex thing

238
00:11:45,200 --> 00:11:48,700
so let's start by using the module we have

239
00:11:49,000 --> 00:11:53,633
and we find out that this is already as good as our 8 blast furnaces together

240
00:11:53,866 --> 00:11:56,166
and while that module works

241
00:11:56,166 --> 00:12:00,000
we are actually increasing the progress of our forge milestones

242
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:05,166
those are goals that once reached will reward us with Graviton Shards

243
00:12:05,166 --> 00:12:07,633
which can be used for more upgrades

244
00:12:07,800 --> 00:12:10,466
after getting all of the basic improvements

245
00:12:10,466 --> 00:12:13,100
we are faced with the first important one

246
00:12:13,266 --> 00:12:16,600
this one will also require some extra materials

247
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:20,033
one of which being lossless photon transfer medium

248
00:12:20,266 --> 00:12:22,300
and long story short

249
00:12:22,300 --> 00:12:27,433
we are going to need to reach a temperature above anything a normal blast furnace could ever reach

250
00:12:27,433 --> 00:12:28,800
17000 Kelvin

251
00:12:28,800 --> 00:12:33,300
and even our helioflare struggles with that at the moment

252
00:12:33,500 --> 00:12:36,400
but we can increase the fuel burn rate of our forge

253
00:12:36,400 --> 00:12:38,266
to reach higher temperatures

254
00:12:38,366 --> 00:12:40,766
now that we can craft those materials

255
00:12:40,766 --> 00:12:42,366
we run into another issue

256
00:12:42,366 --> 00:12:44,033
we don't have enough copper

257
00:12:44,200 --> 00:12:47,300
but we can just pump more with the space elevator

258
00:12:47,466 --> 00:12:48,466
most of that copper

259
00:12:48,466 --> 00:12:51,833
is used in the production of six phased copper nanites

260
00:12:51,900 --> 00:12:56,066
now while that part of the needed material takes a lot of copper

261
00:12:56,066 --> 00:12:59,166
there is one other thing that instead takes a lot of time

262
00:12:59,166 --> 00:13:01,366
transcendent metal nanites

263
00:13:01,466 --> 00:13:04,966
so we can use that time to build more nanoforges

264
00:13:05,233 --> 00:13:06,600
and with that

265
00:13:06,600 --> 00:13:09,566
we have unlocked the helioflux melting core

266
00:13:09,766 --> 00:13:12,800
this module will melt dusts straight into liquid

267
00:13:12,800 --> 00:13:16,433
skipping the need for a vacuum freezer and a fluid extractor

268
00:13:16,600 --> 00:13:18,200
with those two modules

269
00:13:18,200 --> 00:13:22,033
our old blast furnaces can now go into retirement

270
00:13:22,033 --> 00:13:23,866
that will drop a lot of blocks

271
00:13:24,066 --> 00:13:27,100
and also destroy our unbreakable tools

272
00:13:27,100 --> 00:13:29,700
which we can easily craft again

273
00:13:29,700 --> 00:13:30,300
anyways

274
00:13:30,300 --> 00:13:32,033
the next upgrade we can do is

275
00:13:32,033 --> 00:13:35,166
the Gravitational Plasma Containment Inducer

276
00:13:35,166 --> 00:13:38,433
which will unlock the Heliothermal Plasma fabricator

277
00:13:38,466 --> 00:13:41,000
that thing will turn anything into plasma

278
00:13:41,033 --> 00:13:45,200
now that thing is not really worth it for most of the plasma we use

279
00:13:45,200 --> 00:13:51,833
but it can be a great help for some that do require some scarce materials or have low yields in the fusion reactor

280
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:57,066
it will also be the only way to obtain some peculiar plasma required later on

281
00:13:57,366 --> 00:13:57,933
finally

282
00:13:57,933 --> 00:14:01,000
we unlock the Heliofusion excisiter

283
00:14:01,066 --> 00:14:04,000
but that is going to be used only in the next tier

284
00:14:04,200 --> 00:14:06,466
and now we are stuck at the split

285
00:14:06,600 --> 00:14:09,866
here we can chose only one of the three paths

286
00:14:09,966 --> 00:14:12,166
while we decide which path to take

287
00:14:12,166 --> 00:14:14,200
we can make the last QFTs

288
00:14:14,266 --> 00:14:17,066
which will remove a lot of production chains

289
00:14:17,066 --> 00:14:19,200
that will allow us to do a lot of cleanup

290
00:14:19,200 --> 00:14:21,400
and refactoring of our whole base

291
00:14:21,500 --> 00:14:25,033
so that we will no longer have cable messes lying around

292
00:14:25,200 --> 00:14:25,666
finally

293
00:14:25,666 --> 00:14:28,133
we add a bunch more of Dyson Spheres

294
00:14:28,133 --> 00:14:30,300
to increase our power production

295
00:14:30,566 --> 00:14:31,966
and with that

296
00:14:31,966 --> 00:14:35,300
I think we are finally ready to conclude this episode

297
00:14:35,666 --> 00:14:37,866
so what's the lesson today

298
00:14:38,033 --> 00:14:39,866
if you want to stare at the sun

299
00:14:39,866 --> 00:14:41,766
sunglasses are not enough

300
00:14:41,866 --> 00:14:44,166
you need some specialized equipment

301
00:14:44,166 --> 00:14:46,300
possibly a welding helmet

302
00:14:46,300 --> 00:14:46,900
bye bye

303
00:00:00,433 --> 00:00:01,633
欢迎回来

304
00:00:01,966 --> 00:00:05,166
今天我们要进入UMV电压

305
00:00:05,266 --> 00:00:07,633
然而，在做这些之前

306
00:00:07,633 --> 00:00:10,033
我们必须增加发电

307
00:00:10,033 --> 00:00:12,633

虽然看上去风平浪静


308
00:00:12,633 --> 00:00:14,200
实则不然

309
00:00:14,400 --> 00:00:17,033
无线电网可没有电

310
00:00:17,100 --> 00:00:20,366
都空到不能支持蓝搅拌工作了

311
00:00:20,366 --> 00:00:23,400

它才刚充了10分钟的电


312
00:00:23,400 --> 00:00:25,566

就马上把它用光了


313
00:00:25,766 --> 00:00:28,500
所以我们将建造第二个戴森球

314
00:00:28,500 --> 00:00:30,200
由于不会是最后一个

315
00:00:30,200 --> 00:00:33,200

而且每一个都需要许多不同的部分/方块


316
00:00:33,200 --> 00:00:35,233
我们定制一个样板

317
00:00:35,233 --> 00:00:38,500
只需单击一下即可准备其所有组件

318
00:00:38,566 --> 00:00:38,900

在下单面板上


319
00:00:38,900 --> 00:00:42,200

我们有这些结构的总成本


320
00:00:42,200 --> 00:00:44,000
一旦结构建成

321
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:45,466
我们可以回基地了

322
00:00:45,466 --> 00:00:46,200

别忘了


323
00:00:46,200 --> 00:00:48,800
我们也有后备隐藏能源

324
00:00:48,800 --> 00:00:50,266

来额外发电


325
00:00:50,300 --> 00:00:50,633
可惜

326
00:00:50,633 --> 00:00:54,100

我们的发电量没能达到1万亿EU/t的里程碑


327
00:00:54,266 --> 00:00:54,933
不要害怕

328
00:00:54,933 --> 00:00:57,433
这是硅岩燃料的终点

329
00:00:57,433 --> 00:01:00,000
但它仍然未来可期

330
00:01:00,200 --> 00:01:02,600
随着燃料的升级

331
00:01:02,600 --> 00:01:05,033

我们几乎可以达到2万亿EU/t发电


332
00:01:05,166 --> 00:01:07,833
现在我们有了更多的电力

333
00:01:07,833 --> 00:01:10,033

我们着手完成新任务


334
00:01:10,166 --> 00:01:12,900

在快速做完常规的部件后


335
00:01:12,900 --> 00:01:16,400
我们可能想升级部件装配线

336
00:01:16,400 --> 00:01:19,666
以降低时空和海珀珍成本

337
00:01:19,766 --> 00:01:20,466
然而

338
00:01:20,466 --> 00:01:23,600
看来我们不缺硬质金属

339
00:01:23,700 --> 00:01:27,066
我们缺少外星细菌制造的聚合物

340
00:01:27,233 --> 00:01:28,700
要跳过整个化学过程

341
00:01:28,700 --> 00:01:30,800
我们需要四级量子操纵者

342
00:01:30,800 --> 00:01:34,333
然而，这需要太多的UMV组件

343
00:01:34,333 --> 00:01:36,400
所以我们回到超净间

344
00:01:36,400 --> 00:01:38,200

在这变异更多细菌


345
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:40,833
然后放入新的培养缸

346
00:01:40,900 --> 00:01:41,766
同时

347
00:01:41,766 --> 00:01:44,766
我们可以生产一些高级材料

348
00:01:44,766 --> 00:01:47,266
给电路装配加一步

349
00:01:47,366 --> 00:01:50,466
我们得到了最后的UMV组件

350
00:01:50,566 --> 00:01:52,633
然后我们制造新的超导

351
00:01:52,633 --> 00:01:54,033
来做新的能源仓

352
00:01:54,033 --> 00:01:56,200
能源仓现在可以做无线版本了

353
00:01:56,300 --> 00:01:58,066
想得到它

354
00:01:58,066 --> 00:02:01,366
全阶段的无线仓都得做一遍

355
00:02:01,400 --> 00:02:05,300
让我们先停下，回到梦开始的地方

356
00:02:05,366 --> 00:02:06,233
首先

357
00:02:06,233 --> 00:02:08,600
我们需要新的超导

358
00:02:08,666 --> 00:02:12,266
这次包含龙血和时空

359
00:02:12,566 --> 00:02:14,400
使其超导

360
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:16,433
氦气已经落伍

361
00:02:16,566 --> 00:02:18,500
必须使用时空

362
00:02:18,766 --> 00:02:22,400
但这样只能做出普通的UMV能源仓

363
00:02:22,500 --> 00:02:24,000
使其无线化

364
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:26,233
除了一堆昂贵的东西

365
00:02:26,233 --> 00:02:28,300
我们需要做一些研究

366
00:02:28,366 --> 00:02:29,800

非常套娃的研究


367
00:02:29,966 --> 00:02:33,433
一直到ULV无线能量仓

368
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:36,400
尽管我们有UMV能源仓

369
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:38,633
我们没有ULV的

370
00:02:38,866 --> 00:02:39,966
一旦我们得到它

371
00:02:39,966 --> 00:02:42,633

我们必须研究和制作所有其他电压的能源仓


372
00:02:42,633 --> 00:02:44,266
一路到UMV

373
00:02:44,633 --> 00:02:47,100
由于我们的数据库插槽有限

374
00:02:47,100 --> 00:02:49,566
我们懒得做第二个

375
00:02:49,566 --> 00:02:53,200
我们把所有没用的东西都装进箱子里

376
00:02:53,200 --> 00:02:55,466
现在它几乎满了

377
00:02:55,600 --> 00:02:58,233

然后没有更多套娃


378
00:02:58,233 --> 00:03:02,600

我们就获得了迄今最强的无线能源仓


379
00:03:02,633 --> 00:03:04,900
64A UMV无线能源仓

380
00:03:05,066 --> 00:03:09,000
它和16,384A UV激光源仓一样强力

381
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:10,433
但它是无线的

382
00:03:10,433 --> 00:03:14,166
它的第一个用途是加速电路生产

383
00:03:14,566 --> 00:03:18,233
这样我们就可以每分钟制造一个以上的UXV电路

384
00:03:18,233 --> 00:03:20,500
而不是每15分钟一个

385
00:03:20,766 --> 00:03:21,600
同时

386
00:03:21,600 --> 00:03:25,233
我们升级了部件装配线

387
00:03:25,366 --> 00:03:27,366
下一个任务不是真正的任务

388
00:03:27,366 --> 00:03:28,366
而是一个警告

389
00:03:28,566 --> 00:03:31,266
我们可以简单地把它标记为完成然后继续前进

390
00:03:31,266 --> 00:03:34,033
但我认为我们应该升级基地

391
00:03:34,066 --> 00:03:35,833
确实，从现在开始

392
00:03:35,833 --> 00:03:39,900
要做一些戴森球还很困难

393
00:03:40,033 --> 00:03:41,666
这可不是好消息

394
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:45,900
我们首先要解决的是拉多X聚合物

395
00:03:46,200 --> 00:03:49,666
我们的主要目标是用QFT来生产它

396
00:03:50,100 --> 00:03:52,600
但那需要四级外壳

397
00:03:52,600 --> 00:03:55,033
第三级的我们都不好做

398
00:03:55,766 --> 00:03:59,833
所以拉多X的旧产线必须扩大

399
00:04:00,166 --> 00:04:02,666
幸亏有洛基戒指

400
00:04:02,700 --> 00:04:05,466
我们可以同时制造许多机器

401
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:08,033
现在我们只需要再等一会儿

402
00:04:08,033 --> 00:04:10,066
来存储拉多X

403
00:04:10,366 --> 00:04:12,866

四级QFT需要的另一个材料是


404
00:04:12,866 --> 00:04:15,566
超固态超能硅岩黑体

405
00:04:15,566 --> 00:04:17,800
这是在超能硅岩的处理中产生的

406
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:21,400
这个过程输出一些惰性硅岩粉

407
00:04:21,400 --> 00:04:23,500
数量可能看起来不大

408
00:04:23,500 --> 00:04:28,400
但我们可以用中子活化器将其扩展成数千锭

409
00:04:28,633 --> 00:04:32,133
转换的唯一成本是一点等离子体和时间

410
00:04:32,133 --> 00:04:37,633
我们可以通过增加中子活化器的高度来缩短时间

411
00:04:38,033 --> 00:04:41,033

因此，我们让它突破天际


412
00:04:41,300 --> 00:04:43,566
三级QFT已经完成

413
00:04:43,900 --> 00:04:44,833
要做四级的

414
00:04:45,200 --> 00:04:47,033
我们需要更多的拉多X聚合物

415
00:04:47,366 --> 00:04:48,800
在它囤积的同时

416
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:52,300
我们可以收集缺少的其他材料

417
00:04:52,433 --> 00:04:56,033
我们的旧太空电梯无法储存足够的液体

418
00:04:56,033 --> 00:04:58,700

所以我们升级了它的加速轨道和泵


419
00:04:58,966 --> 00:05:01,966
虽然这很容易解决缺失的液体

420
00:05:01,966 --> 00:05:04,233
但缺矿问题却不会改善

421
00:05:04,366 --> 00:05:07,266
有些矿石不能通过太空开采获得

422
00:05:07,500 --> 00:05:10,033
所以我们必须回到虚采

423
00:05:10,300 --> 00:05:13,600
但我们想把它们放在更特别的地方

424
00:05:13,700 --> 00:05:16,800
只有像我们这种真正的中二病才会选的地方

425
00:05:17,100 --> 00:05:18,233

要到达那个地方


426
00:05:18,233 --> 00:05:21,466
我们得从压缩大量圆石开始

427
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:24,700
聚爆必须升级

428
00:05:24,700 --> 00:05:26,600
升级至时空块和使用80亿EU

429
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:29,200
才能在合理的时间内压缩圆石

430
00:05:29,433 --> 00:05:31,966
我们将圆石涂上奶酪

431
00:05:31,966 --> 00:05:34,866
这将充当其他组件的胶水

432
00:05:34,866 --> 00:05:35,633
终于

433
00:05:35,633 --> 00:05:40,100
我们用魔法把一些奇点粘在凝集物上

434
00:05:40,100 --> 00:05:40,800
有了那个

435
00:05:40,800 --> 00:05:42,966
我们现在可以去到应许之地

436
00:05:42,966 --> 00:05:47,200

在那里虚采可以采掘出所有NEI里有的矿物


437
00:05:47,466 --> 00:05:52,066
我们将其与矿处子网进行连接

438
00:05:52,066 --> 00:05:55,000
开始开采这些材料

439
00:05:55,266 --> 00:05:59,000
同时我们已经完成了四级QFT

440
00:05:59,166 --> 00:06:02,433
它现在正在制造大量的拉多X聚合物

441
00:06:02,933 --> 00:06:05,800
既然拉多X已不再是问题

442
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:10,400
我们终于可以开始制作10个戴森球的小工程了

443
00:06:10,633 --> 00:06:11,133
然而

444
00:06:11,133 --> 00:06:14,433
我们现在的基地无法应付那个微不足道的任务

445
00:06:14,566 --> 00:06:16,633
我们必须做一些升级

446
00:06:16,666 --> 00:06:20,266
首先要升级的是高炉

447
00:06:20,366 --> 00:06:21,866

一些材料


448
00:06:21,866 --> 00:06:24,466
每秒只能产出四个锭

449
00:06:24,466 --> 00:06:26,900
积压的工作真的很多

450
00:06:26,933 --> 00:06:30,000
所以进去检查后

451
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:32,033
我们决定采取的最佳行动

452
00:06:32,033 --> 00:06:34,833
是给线圈加一些闪光

453
00:06:34,966 --> 00:06:37,500
以及加点电进去

454
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:40,366
现在它的工作速度快了8倍

455
00:06:40,433 --> 00:06:44,033
接下来要加速的是聚变反应堆

456
00:06:44,100 --> 00:06:46,266
MK3一直很慢

457
00:06:46,266 --> 00:06:49,966
MK4忙着做亚稳态鿫

458
00:06:50,133 --> 00:06:53,000
所以我们要做Mk5聚变反应堆

459
00:06:53,066 --> 00:06:57,700
你可以从它的颜色中看出它强得可怕

460
00:06:57,833 --> 00:07:00,833

而且它确实跟10个MK 4的效率差不多


461
00:07:01,100 --> 00:07:03,566
对于快速配方

462
00:07:03,566 --> 00:07:06,100
我们可以手动设置并行

463
00:07:06,400 --> 00:07:09,833
因此它比MK3快100倍

464
00:07:10,400 --> 00:07:13,100
接下来是空冷塔

465
00:07:13,100 --> 00:07:17,233
我们让PCB工厂加快2000倍

466
00:07:17,566 --> 00:07:20,066
然后是纳米锻炉

467
00:07:20,066 --> 00:07:22,166
我们建造了更多这样的建筑

468
00:07:22,166 --> 00:07:24,666
同时也增加了工作功率

469
00:07:24,866 --> 00:07:27,066
最终是我们的DTPF

470
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:29,566
我们又加了四个

471
00:07:29,766 --> 00:07:34,000
但所有这些都导致了电力消耗的巨大增加

472
00:07:34,400 --> 00:07:36,200

为了升级硅岩发电


473
00:07:36,200 --> 00:07:38,100
我们添加两种液体

474
00:07:38,100 --> 00:07:39,366
来提高燃料效率

475
00:07:39,366 --> 00:07:41,733
这些液体是通过在锻造锤上

476
00:07:41,733 --> 00:07:45,866
用超立方体和量子反常来撕裂时空获得

477
00:07:46,200 --> 00:07:50,433
这一提升足以让我们完成最后一个蓝搅拌配方

478
00:07:50,433 --> 00:07:53,533
从而在我们耗尽燃料之前

479
00:07:53,533 --> 00:07:55,233
建成新发电机

480
00:07:55,433 --> 00:07:58,833
旧戴森球占用了相当大的空间

481
00:07:58,833 --> 00:08:02,233
所以我们新设计一种紧凑的方案

482
00:08:02,366 --> 00:08:05,766
我们发现可以共享一堆零件

483
00:08:05,966 --> 00:08:08,966
最重要的是算力输入

484
00:08:09,066 --> 00:08:11,500
我们现在将使其无线化

485
00:08:11,500 --> 00:08:13,600

与云端连接


486
00:08:13,900 --> 00:08:19,100

这样我们就能把计算机留在主基地规划好的数据中心


487
00:08:19,466 --> 00:08:20,566
有了那个设置

488
00:08:20,566 --> 00:08:22,700
我们现在正在产生更多的能量

489
00:08:22,700 --> 00:08:25,966
但对于升级后的基地也只是堪堪满足

490
00:08:26,100 --> 00:08:29,433
所以很明显我们需要更多

491
00:08:29,700 --> 00:08:31,833
但是有一个主要问题

492
00:08:31,833 --> 00:08:35,066
我们生产转转锭的速度太慢了

493
00:08:35,166 --> 00:08:38,366
EBF每秒都生产不了两个

494
00:08:38,366 --> 00:08:39,800
而需要的数量以百万计

495
00:08:39,800 --> 00:08:41,666
抱着找到解法的希望

496
00:08:41,666 --> 00:08:44,300
我们应该去求助一些随机的村民

497
00:08:44,300 --> 00:08:47,266
他们似乎在崇拜一些随机的神

498
00:08:47,500 --> 00:08:49,833
看来我们的祈祷得到了回应

499
00:08:49,833 --> 00:08:53,433

我们要做的就是建造一个致敬神的锻炉


500
00:08:53,433 --> 00:08:54,500
我们要把它做大一点

501
00:08:54,500 --> 00:08:58,366
并且比我们迄今为止构建的任何其他多方块都更复杂

502
00:08:58,366 --> 00:08:59,666
制作它

503
00:08:59,666 --> 00:09:02,366
